	   <tr><td colspan=2>lvl 55 is a great time to go to chardok.&nbsp;&nbsp;kill the entrance mobs for great exp and some occasional (OCCASIONAL) good loot. You can always try for a group, move in, and get some really nice stuff/exp.  luclin also has some soloing spots, a good mage can solo in the grey.  you can always be classic and kill in velks and seb too.<br><br>Personally, i think items can make all the difference, boots of bladecalling or a burnt wood staff are a must.  velious/PoG robe is great too for your pets...i havent noticed a huge difference between cadeau and lava for pets.  <br>JBOOTS! or innate runspeed3 can and will save your ass repetetively.<br>thats all i got, work on those boots :)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Faberin Midgetpunter<br>61 Magician<br>Tunare</td></tr>
