	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.65]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The focus items do indeed work on pet summons from level 4 to 49. If you can somehow manage to get them at lvl 4, they will work at lvl 4.<br><br>The focus items increase the stats of your pets, not their levels. A lot of the confusion about them only working after 34 is because at 34 using a focus noticably increases the size of your pet. However I got my foci at about level 24 (if I remember right) and I did notice a signifigant difference between focused and non focused pets.<br><br>A lot of people have researched this one, with much more attention to detail than I have, and they've all concured.<br><br>Post 49 you need the staves of elemental mastery which all drop off of raid level bosses.<br><br><br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, the Mad Mage of Povar<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
