	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a mage, the best partner I have found was a necro.&nbsp;&nbsp;Being DE, a necro friend should be fairly easy to find.  The necro is dotting and fearing.  You are nuking.  Both pets are tanking and sharing aggro.  As long as the pets keep aggro, the only ones needing healing is the pets, so no cleric/shaman/druid needed.  I have found that the air pet or earth pet works best.  The fire pet is the worst since the skelton pet should have aggro every other mob so the fire pet's greatest attribute is not being taken advantage. LOL, although I am sure others disagree.<br><br>GL<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
